%div.what.first
  %p Do you want to share your knowledge and thoughts?
  %p ... but you don't want to get into a blogging platform.
  %p 
    Are you familiar with 
    %a{:href => 'http://www.evernote.com', :target => '_blank'} Evernote?
  %p Would you believe me if I tell you that you will have a blog in less than 5 minutes (even less if you already have an Evernote account)?
  %p Give it a try!!

%div.what.what-reverse
  %p Open your Evernote.
  %p Create a notebook with the name you would like for your blog.
  %p Make the notebook public.

%div.what
  %p Create a new note in your blog notebook.
  %p Give it a title.
  %p That will be the title of your first post.
  %p Insert some text.
  %p Attach a picture to the note.

%div.what.what-reverse
  %form{ :method => 'POST', :action => '/blogify', :name => 'url_form', :id => 'url_form'}
    %label Insert the blog notebook public url.
    %div.input-append
      %input{ :placeholder => "http://www.evernote.com/pub/user/notebook", :name => 'publicUrl', :id => 'publicUrl'}
    %button{ :type => 'submit', :id => "submit", :class => "btn arrange"}
      %div{ :id => "imgBtnDiv", :width => "15px", :height => "15px"}
        %img{ :src => 'img/arrange.png', :alt => 'Arrange', :id => "submitImg"}